{"tid":2174157,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"改善公眾認知 男神矢志帶領屋宇設備工程業界更上一層樓","createTime":"2020-08-25T17:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T11:47:42.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77319923b70ce682b0117ff65075a0d833286dbf","tid":2174157,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"2019年屋宇設備工程學士課程的畢業生郭梓賢（Jack）畢業後參加了香港工程師學會的工程畢業生培訓計劃(Scheme A)，現在於工程顧問公司擔任見習工程師。已經工作了約1年的Jack表示，課程所學到的知識都幫助他適應工作。「投身行業後發現原來很多公司都使用包括BIM技術，課堂所學到的各項技術都有助我更快適應工作。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5c7h8vf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5c7h8vf.jpg&h=ad4d51c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對同學而言，畢業前累積實戰經驗和了解行業資訊同樣重要，因此課程為同學提供不少於3個月工作實習，讓同學掌握業界實況。Roger指，課程更獲得香港工程師學會（The Hong Kong Institution of Engineers, HKIE）認可，同學畢業後可參加簡稱Scheme A的工程畢業生培訓計劃，最快4年便可考獲專業工程師資格。「<strong>根據2019年THEi的畢業生就業調查，屋宇設備工程學士課程第一届畢業生的就業率為99%，畢業生平均起薪點更接近2萬元</strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8n2Aay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8n2Aay.jpg&h=c31d88cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJack表示課程不只提供實習機會，還提供不少海外交流的機會。「我曾到新加坡和當地的工程師交流，了解當地的專業水平和最新工程科技，令我大開眼界。」Jack 亦曾於環保能源公司實習，了解綠色能源最新技術。他坦言，這些實習和海外交流機會除了讓他獲得不少的實戰經驗，更啓發了他未來的工作目標。「長遠而言，我想在未來成為一個有影響力的工程師，與工程業一同邁向更好將來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpriSWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpriSWV.jpg&h=62802878&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40164de59cbfa83afc40318843098daecefa7620","tid":2174157,"uid":225931,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71521c96493418d1c8c0ffc49d23e8b700ff94d7","tid":2174157,"uid":342929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:47:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ff14d57a41e297c7808ddce4f006710fc1dac3","tid":2174157,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9413acbbbd50040b6b6e1f274597f6b7b646621f","tid":2174157,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:45:01.000Z","msg":"up test"},{"pid":"e0120ecd7e2b05cb096a5a57808db28cc0283462","tid":2174157,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"邊撚個啊"},{"pid":"e4b8040d9049361fcca0f4a0bb39a4b48a793638","tid":2174157,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"2萬好正常者<br />\n<br />\n而家邊個工程畢業生冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd野又難讀"}]}